window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>As undead hordes roam the frozen landscape, a lone man squares off against an even deadlier foe, in the gritty conclusion to this werewolf horror series.</b></p> <p>Douglas Kirk is having a bad week. Not only are humans hunting him, but whole packs of werewolves have been commanded to kill him on sight, forcing him to flee Halifax without identification, money, weapons, even his phone.</p> <p>If he wants to survive, he'll have to evade the killers on his trail, travel across the country to confront the elusive elders, and learn the truth behind the order that made him what he is. All he has to do is control his insatiable hunger for wereflesh just a little longer . . .</p> <p><i>Breeds 3</i> is the third book in this terrifying series sure to please fans of Robert R. McCammon, Maggie Stiefvater, and Chase Novak.</p>"; 
